txt.en: 'The vile chieftain of the wargs, Drokstaz, may be banished, but his kin remain and they are no less a threat than he was! Kasak and Dúlkoth were born of the same litter, and now they seek to avenge their sire. They have come down from the mountains and will stop at nothing less than to feast upon any of Duskenvale's folk that might smile at the banishment of Drokstaz. Defeat these two brother-wargs, and quickly, for their ranging is swift and their anger deep.'
Defeat Kasak and Dúlkoth, the kin of Drokstaz.
The Beorning Ragnild is concerned about the threat posed by the wargs of Duskenvale.
